# Client bootstrap

For setup, deployment, handoff, or fresh-stack provisioning:

1. Read [docs/HANDOFF.md](../../docs/HANDOFF.md)
2. Follow [.cursor/skills/clutch-bootstrap/SKILL.md](../skills/clutch-bootstrap/SKILL.md)
3. Use the Vercel plugin / CLI — do not hardcode another team's project name
4. Run `npm run bootstrap:check` after `vercel env pull`
5. Never print secret env values

Only modify application code if bootstrap verification reveals a product bug, not as part of initial provisioning.
